Throughput remains stable; Latency scales with epoll batch size

ol.li: Linear Range (0-8k): Latency remains flat (<5ms). epoll_wait batches are small.
Saturation Knee (~8.5k): Interrupt coalescing and rdllist processing time starts to exceed loop cycle time.
Queuing Delay (>9k): Gradual increase in p99 as epoll_wait processing time grows linearly with active events per tick.
